      "para_id": "Q005018.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the protective god of his land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , presented this ( seal ) to Urim-kidug , the king's cook , his servant ."
    }
